column1: Baby Barnaby's////The OJ! Delicious (fresh squeezed)! The breakfast was pretty darn good too! All the staff were very nice
column2: and the place was hopping busy but they were attentive
column3: cheerful and not rushing people out. I recommend you get the potatoes with your order! And I can vouch for the bacon
column4: it's the good stuff. The toast is thick & chewy & there is real chilled butter and a caddy of yummy jams right on your table.
